column2: SELECT TOP #   A.UIIID,A.RAJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER,A.DEJ2#WISE_AGN_R9#_ptsrc_VIZIER, 									 B.z,B.zerr,B.class,B.subClass,B.specObjID,C.specObjID as specObjIDClean,B.ObjID, 					ABS(A.petroMag_uSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_u) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_gSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_g) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_rSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_r) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_iSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_i) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_zSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_z) 					FROM 					  MyDB.CasjobsCombinedOutputBrief AS A, SpecPhotoAll AS B 					  LEFT JOIN SpecObj as C ON B.specObjID=C.specObjID 					WHERE 					  A.petroMag_uSDSSDR1#!=&&& 					  AND B.class!=&&& 					  AND ABS(A.petroMag_uSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_u)<=# 					  AND ABS(A.petroMag_gSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_g)<=# 					  AND ABS(A.petroMag_rSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_r)<=# 					  AND ABS(A.petroMag_iSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_i)<=# 					  AND ABS(A.petroMag_zSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_z)<=# 					  AND A.UIIID=#ORDER BY  					   ABS(A.petroMag_uSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_u) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_gSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_g) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_rSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_r) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_iSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_i) 					  +ABS(A.petroMag_zSDSSDR1#-B.petroMag_z) 					INTO 					   MyDB.CasjobsCombinedOutputBrief_SpecPhotoAll_MagSpace1#
